{"id": "art-488", "label": "Art. 488", "title": "Art. 488: Calea de atac", "slug": "art-488", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 488: Calea de atac </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2092139319\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1342\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2092139319\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Împotriva sentin&#355;ei pronun&#355;ate potrivit art.\n485 &#351;i 486, procurorul, inculpatul, celelalte p&#259;r&#355;i &#351;i\npersoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; pot declara apel, în termen de 10 zile de la\ncomunicare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_183078526\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1341\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_183078526\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Apelul poate fi declarat în condi&#355;iile art. 409,\ncare se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_916366984\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1340\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_916366984\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La solu&#355;ionarea apelului se citeaz&#259;\np&#259;r&#355;ile &#351;i persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1788107173\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1339\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1788107173\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Instan&#355;a de\napel pronun&#355;&#259; una dintre urm&#259;toarele solu&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_187695873\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1338\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_187695873\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)respinge apelul, men&#355;inând hot&#259;rârea\natacat&#259;, dac&#259; apelul este tardiv sau inadmisibil ori nefondat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_467409893\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1337\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_467409893\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)admite apelul, desfiin&#355;eaz&#259; sentin&#355;a prin\ncare acordul de recunoa&#351;tere a fost admis &#351;i pronun&#355;&#259; o\nnou&#259; hot&#259;râre, procedând potrivit art. 485 &#351;i 486, care se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1831445010\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1336\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1831445010\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)admite apelul, desfiin&#355;eaz&#259; sentin&#355;a prin\ncare acordul de recunoa&#351;tere a fost respins, admite acordul de\nrecunoa&#351;tere a vinov&#259;&#355;iei, dispozi&#355;iile art. 485 alin. (1)\nlit. a) &#351;i art. 486 aplicându-se în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_1915923519\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1335\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1915923519\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL I<sup>1</sup>:Contesta&#355;ia\nprivind durata procesului penal</span></b></p>"}